fields.name: MatchVariable
fields.description: The variable to be scrubbed from the logs.

fields.name: Selector
fields.description: When matchVariable is a collection, operator used to specify which elements in the collection this rule applies to.

fields.name: SelectorMatchOperator
fields.description: When matchVariable is a collection, operate on the selector to specify which elements in the collection this rule applies to.

fields.name: State
fields.description: Defines the state of log scrubbing rule. Default value is Enabled.
